Why not just have the 1/3 gold for not last hitting a minion? It'd basically make lane bullies less problematic and would elimate the need for supports to purchase an item in order to get gold. which always bothered me because it makes it so support items need to be busted to be viable thus making tons of super efficient cheap items that wind up getting abused by others in certain metas
{{item:3504}} {{item:3109}} 

also eliminates the severity of raging adcs who experience the immense trauma that is brand/sona/raka adc poking and accidentally last hitting a minion
